oc_lettings_siteÔÉÅ

Contains all modules of the lettings app

Modules :

  • admin : django main admin configuration

  • apps : django apps configuration

  • asgi : django asgi settings configuration

  • settings : app settings

  • tests : app tests module

  • urls : app url router

  • views : app views

  • wsgi : django wsgi settings configuration
